 * description: 展示产品/应用的核心优势，三列卡片布局
 * category: content
 * region: content
 * thumbnail: asset/img/our-advantages/icon01.webp
 * @component_end
 * 
 * @fields_start
 * 
 * group:advantages => 优势区域设置
